			'The Best Arugula Pesto takes roughly <b>45 minutes</b> from beginning to end. For <b>91 cents per serving</b>, this recipe <b>covers 7%</b> of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. This recipe serves 6. This condiment has <b>139 calories</b>, <b>6g of protein</b>, and <b>12g of fat</b> per serving. 3 people found this recipe to be scrumptious and satisfying. A mixture of arugula, extra virgin olive oil, salt, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so scrumptious. It is a good option if you\'re following a <b>gluten free, primal, and ketogenic</b> diet. It is brought to you by Foodista. With a spoonacular <b>score of 45%</b>, this dish is solid. Try <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/arugula-pesto-pesto-di-rucola-300106">Arugula Pesto: Pesto Di Rucola</a>, <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/arugula-pesto-910971">Arugula Pesto</a>, and <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/arugula-pesto-1293871">Arugula Pesto</a> for similar recipes.',
